{"id":1163957,"date":[{"year":1998,"month":8,"day":21}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"画刊","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"296","ytitle":"","mtitle":"邓小平","ftitle":"——女儿心中的父亲","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040201.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>邓林</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>回眸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知道是什么吸引了爸爸的目光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京玉泉山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1987年5月·83岁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040202.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>退休日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中央正式批准爸爸退休，四个孙子特意为爷爷制作了贺卡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上面写着:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“愿爷爷永远和我们一样年青!!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是爷爷和孙辈们在看贺卡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京家中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1989年11月9日·85岁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040203.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>“步子再快一点”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广东省珠海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1992年1月·88岁<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040204.JPG\">雪后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸喜欢雪，他说有雪庄稼才能长得好。那一年，上海下了一场多年未见的雪，爸爸高兴地在雪中留影。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1988年1月·84岁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040205.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>题字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爸爸在为楠楠题字:“善学者其如海。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河北省北戴河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1984年·80岁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040206.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>亲亲爷爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京家中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1992年8月22日·88岁</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入12号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1998\\08\\988l040207.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>永不停步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1993年12月·89岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"邓林/摄影</FONT>"}]}